steps.name: And the user clicks on the Skip to calculator link
Then the user should be able to see the Mortgage Payment Calculator form
When the user enters a purchase price of 750000
And the user enters a down payment of 25
And the user enters an interest rate of 3.8
And the user selects "7 year fixed closed" as the term
And the user selects "Accelerated Biweekly" as the payment frequency
And the user clicks the Calculate button
Then the user should be able to scroll down and see the results section
